{"tid":1775962,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"花旗：近半港人睇淡未來一年樓價 約六成無興趣置業","createTime":"2019-12-09T07:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T08:16:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e19eccd9457e29e82dabf97ad4a3628f673b676c","tid":1775962,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2019/12/09/xujiachun_1f52f20b9a2c73f0906d9e51bb04f51c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2019%2F12%2F09%2Fxujiachun_1f52f20b9a2c73f0906d9e51bb04f51c.jpg&h=57b8cf05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行今日（9日)公布2019年第四季香港市民置業意向調查，結果顯示受訪者普遍對樓市持觀望態度，46%受訪者預期樓價將在未來12個月下跌，比例按季降10%，反映整體看淡樓市的受訪者比例下跌。<br />\n<br />\n不過受訪者入市意欲仍低迷，57%表示現時對置業非常不感興趣或頗不感興趣，按季上升6%，而對置業持高度興趣的受訪者僅佔16%，比例較上季微跌4%。另一方面，60%受訪者表示現時非置業理想時機，但比例較上季下跌8%。<br />\n<br />\n是項調查為花旗銀行委託香港大學社會科學研究中心，以隨機抽樣電話訪問形式，在2019年10月訪問超過500名香港市民。"},{"pid":"f54d5bbc3b55b20d67586275aac4075266c7a2cd","tid":1775962,"uid":162008,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"周圍全球通脹升緊，就算短期睇淡，一升返上黎就不得了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"9a8de69bbfbefe8e6d558dd3195d6edea7303370","tid":1775962,"uid":19217,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"你唔買大把人買<br />\n宜家唔買 <br />\n遲d上車升到800萬添啊"},{"pid":"ce20cd11618a8cff0f7855751766ff0cefad8934","tid":1775962,"uid":25538,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"貴到唔想買<br />\n訓街好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c0df1a270c3853793191e0f7ba1f6c438f0c75","tid":1775962,"uid":58931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"樓價downdowndown<img src=\"/assets/face